refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public mixedpht\Vector::shift
This method shifts a value from the front of a vector (in linear time). Shifting a value from an empty vector will result in an Error exception.

  &reftitle.examples;



    Shifting a value from a vector


<?php

use pht\Vector;

$vector = new Vector();

$vector->push(1);
$vector[] = 2;

var_dump($vector->shift());


    &example.outputs;


int(1)
